ActSpecies at Risk Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the Species at Risk Act
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE 1 TO THE SPECIES AT RISK ACT in order to help maintain Canada’s biodiversity and the well-being of Canadian ecosystems by preventing wildlife species from becoming extirpated from Canada or extinct and contribute to their recovery, as well as to respond to Committee on the Status of Endangered Wildlife in Canada’s recommendations.
